Eagle

High in the sky— 
A stoic figure roams,
This grand bird
In experienced flight,
With daunting grace it seals the air
Above the hilltops, 
Riding rapture and fire,
O | Eagle—I shadow behind,
Wind within your wings,
Luminous soaring through
the vibrant expanse of day.

— H.D. (Hilda Doolittle)

- HD
